===Etymology===
From {{etyl|xno|en}} {{term|Espayne|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|LL.|en}} {{term|Spania|lang=la}}, from earlier {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|Hispānia|lang=la}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{term|tr=Hispania|Ἱσπανία|lang=grc}}, from {{etyl|phn|en}} {{term|tr=ay-shaphanim|lang=phn|sc=Phnx|lit=[[hyrax]] isle}}, as the native wild rabbits were mistaken for hyraces.

